Shockwave/Punch/Double Punch/Breakdown/Hiss/Pyro:


Hiss fired off three fusion blasts from his cannon at Hot Rod, taking flight.

Breakdown rolled, transforming to robot mode and running after Hiss.

Double Punch fired off two energy signature seeking missiles form his 
pinchers, one at Steel, the other at Ripper, taking flight.

Punch ran, running into the depths of the forest that hadn't been burn.

Pyro turned his cannon in an arc, firing a 'continuous' burst off flames off 
at Ripper, Steel, and Archangel.  Powering up his engines, his treads sent 
Pyro backwards, driving away from the fight, ceasing fire, targeting with his 
cannon just in case, set on fireball mode.

Shockwave saw the Predacons disappate, and ran for the clearing so he could 
take flight.
